import java.util.*;
//String Builders->Since strings are immutable in nature so any kind of updation took a long time bcoz of which we required more optimized 
//string class named String Builder which can perform any updation in string with less time and hence for any updation we use string builder
//In strings as we update anything str changes its reference whereas in string builder str points to same and updation happens at same reference

public class Main
